Zik-nni tirugza tesɛa azal d ameqran mačči d amecṭuḥ.
Argaz yesɛa lhiba, tameṭṭut tesɛa sser.
Winna s wacu i ttgallan meṛṛa yirgazen.
Taqbaylit mi ara tger abernus, tettnawal seksu deg uxxam-is.
Ad d-tawi tiwiziwin ara tt-iɛiwnen ad textir lexyar di tlawin.
Tid i yessnen azeṭṭa akken iwulem.
Ad d-nezzi,ad nettwali.
Amzun akken d tameɣra i nga deg uxxam-nneɣ.
Yemma akked tlawin-nni ad ssefruyent, ad sbuɣurent.
Sɛant yiwen n ṣṣut i d-yettarra udrar.
Ay ḥemmleɣ tibuɣarin n yemma.
Aksum-iw yettciriw.
Allen-iw ttaččarent-d d immeṭṭi.
Ṣṣut ḥninen mačči d kra.
Nesɛa tazeqqa tmeqqer nezzeh.
Dinna i neggan meṛṛa.
Abernus-nni dinna i t-teggar yemma.
Ad skecmaɣ iḍudan-iw daxel n lexyuḍ-nni n uẓeṭṭa.
Yemma ad iyi-tewwet
Win i yegganen daxel n uzeṭṭa, ad d-yas ɣur-s buberrak.
Ad d-yeẓẓel afus-is aɣezzfan ad t-yawi yid-s.
Ar tura xas akka meqqreɣ, ttaggadeɣ buberrak.
Ttamneɣ ayen akk i d-teqqar yemma.
Imeslayen-iw i kečč a Masi.
Gma ur d-tesɛi yemma.
Wina akken i ijerḥen ul-iw.
Icerriqen n yiṭij ɛeddan-d si ṭṭaq.
Beddeɣ ɣef ṭṭaq.
Arrac ttazallen ḥafi.
Allen-iw ttrunt, qerḥent-iyi.
Dexxan yesru-d allen-iw.
Ad yeqqim deg umezruy.
Ulac leḥzen, ulac imeṭṭi.
Imeslayen-iw s yidammen-ik uriɣ-ten.
Ɣas gullen ad nɣen.
Ɣas ssensen itran deg tudrin.
Sdereɣlen lebɣi-nni d leḥmala-nni i yettnernin.
Walaɣ-ten gar wallen-iw.
Ceɛlen times.
Mačči di berra.
Rẓan tawwurt, kecmen.
D wa i d axxam-nneɣ.
Ḍeggreɣ-d iman-iw si ṭṭaq.
Ahat ad rewleɣ.
Tezzi-d tmes, si mkul tama.
Teččurem ilem.
Ad d-nerr nnehta.
Imesbaṭliyen d kenwi.
A wid ur nesɛi tissas.
Tudert tehda-aɣ-d.
Tin akken s wacu i nettwali.
Mi akken i ferḥeɣ.
Mi aken i ttruɣ.
Ḥemmleɣ-kem.
Deg-m ɣliɣ, deg-m kkreɣ.
Swiɣ lqaɛa-m s yimeṭṭawen n leǧruḥ-iw.
Deg-m tezzuzen-yi lmeḥna.
Ḥemmleɣ-kem d tacebḥant s udfel.
Ḥemmleɣ-kem deg-m tecɛel tmes.
Ḥemmleɣ-kem s yitran i yettfeǧiǧen.
Ḥemmleɣ-kem s wagu d ṭṭlam.
Ḥemmleɣ-kem ɣas yefqeɛ yigenni.
Caḍeɣ ur swiɣ.
Lluẓeɣ ur ččiɣ.
Ur nessin ara azal-im.
Fell-am tettru tiṭ n win yemmuten.
Win ur nesɛi asirem.
Lukan ad tzewǧeḍ yid-i ad am-sselseɣ tayri-w deg uḍad-im.
Ddunit i yelhan ad am-tt-id muddeɣ.
I lebda ad am fkeɣ lferḥ.
Ad am-buddeɣ ddunit-iw.
I lqerḥ akked lferḥ.
Yal iḍ ad ninig anda yebɣa wul-im.
Ad d-aseɣ ad am-d-awiɣ ciṭ n lferḥ.
Ad kem-ḥadreɣ seg ukukru.
Ad teqqimeḍ deg wul-iw.
Siwa kemm i d tameṭṭut n lebɣi-w.
Teẓriḍ lehḍur-iw ffɣen-d seg wul.
Ad d-ḍelbeɣ afus-im.
Sɛiɣ kan lehḍur-agi.
Ad ten-in-awiɣ yid-i.
Sɛiɣ kan tayri ad am-tt-muddeɣ i lebda.
La ttḥewwiseɣ ur ẓriɣ d acu i ttḥewwiseɣ.
Ur yelli d acu i ufiɣ.
Ffɣeɣ ḍalleɣ ɣer texxamin nniḍen.
Meṛṛa ṭṭsen, ḥala nekk, ayen akka tqelqeɣ?
Ayen akka i yi-iruḥ yiḍes?
Ḍalleɣ si tewwurt walaɣ igenni ifeǧǧeǧ s yitran.
Tiziri tesserɣ-d udem-iw s cbaḥa-s.
Tiziri tuɣal d tameṭṭut.
Imezran ɣef lqaɛa ɣlin.
Ɣur-i teẓẓel-d afus-is.
Ad twaliḍ ayen yeffer zzman ɣef wallen.
Thedder, nek la tt-ttwaliɣ.
Fkiɣ-as afus-iw ur uggadeɣ.
Nezzi-d i yidurar d yiẓuɣaṛ.
Widak i ɣedṛen di lbatel.
Lejdud-im d Imaziɣen, imdanen-nni ilelliyen.
Ẓriɣ tura anwi i d lejdud-iw.
Amzun ukiɣ-d si tnafa.
Qeɛdeɣ iman-iw.
Ad t-lemdeɣ s tmaziɣt.
Yeggul ar d-yerr tamurt-is.
Ad d-yejmaɛ agdud-is.
Ṭṭuqten fell-as yiɛdawen.
Acku uqbel kulci d imdanen i nella.
